  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Tackling modern slavery in DRC: call for bids
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The British Embassy Kinshasa is seeking for projects to tackle modern slavery in the mining sector in DRC for the financial year 2020 to 2021.</p>

  </div>
</div>

